thread.title: Harold Walker
thread.title_full: Maine Lobster Now reviewed by Harold Walker

author: Harold Walker
title: Harold Walker
text: The pre-cooked lobster meet I ordered came in on time The lobster was fresh and full of flavor . What a nice treat while watching the Super Bowl.or for just treating yourself. I bought some from another company that was supposed to be fresh and it wasn't . I will be ordering from this company again for sure and I hope they keep up their quality. Thanks, Maine lobster now.
